Class GardenTile

java.lang.Object
GardenTile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AddOn>
public class GardenTile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<AddOn>, java.io.Serializable
The GardenTile Object which makes up the individual squares on the GardenPlot. They can hold AddOns and contain properties like water and light level as well as soil type

Author:
Bradley
